impactDescription:
We wish to share the impact our contributions had on Optimism Collective:

⭐ ️ Increase in the number of Optimism developers & Web3 eco-system users onboarded to Optimism from 20 to 50 in India. Pilot Deployments at N.S.U.T. campus; S.M.S. School, Delhi;
⭐️Increase in the number of OP developers and contribution to OP stack modules, Governance projects built on OP Stack from 8 to 25;
⭐️Improved collaboration with OP projects like MUD, Wormhole, Base for interoperability.
⭐️ OP solutions for soul bonding ID, interoperability & sharding tools to enable ease of identity management, transparent data movement.
⭐️Decentralizing service governance with oSnap & OP: With offchain voting, human readable rules, & trustless on-chain execution, DAOs can begin to reach their full potential.

